Data cleaning Exlplanations

Data used was accessed on March 17th. Data set is live Removed “Teaninich 10yo (F&F)” before importing because it was missing the Cost variable. Changed “Meta Critic” to “MetaCritic”, “#” to “Num_of_Critics”, “Super Cluster” to “SuperCluster”, “STDEV” to “StDev” to fix coding errors. Added age variable by taking the number of years aged from the Whisky category, signified by #yo in the title of the whisky. In the case of any whiskies with more than one year given, the minimum was taken. (Only example in my dataset “Amrut Greedy Angels (8yo and 10yo)” Other new entries with the same syntax should be treated the same).
